459
00:27:40,992 --> 00:27:43,995
What can we do for Marina?

460
00:28:07,018 --> 00:28:09,220
It's a wonder
that they let us borrow the house.

461
00:28:10,088 --> 00:28:13,158
It isn't unfavorable to the son too.

462
00:28:17,162 --> 00:28:20,732
I don't know what Kurokawa thinks
about this, though.

463
00:28:22,367 --> 00:28:26,371
Mr. Kurokawa,
I think you'd better not do this.

464
00:28:29,374 --> 00:28:32,977
Miss Wakura, stop him with me.
If anything happens…

465
00:28:33,044 --> 00:28:34,379
Thank you.

466
00:28:34,879 --> 00:28:36,081
Everything is ready.

467
00:28:38,817 --> 00:28:40,618
Are you really sure, Kurokawa?

468
00:28:44,689 --> 00:28:46,891
-I'm counting on you.
